short_description: go green store is a plant nursery/store based in india.
long_description: our mission is to inspire and empower people to create their green oasis while championing sustainability in all aspects. as eco-stewards, we prioritize eco-friendly packaging and support responsible sourcing of our products, including an array of plants, pots, and organic essentials like soil, fertilizers, and gardening tools. our plant selection spans a wide variety of species, from air-purifying houseplants to vibrant outdoor flowers and herbs, carefully curated to suit every gardening need and experience level. beyond being an online store, we're a thriving community of eco-conscious individuals offering workshops, gardening advice, and insightful articles on sustainable living. through challenges and triumphs, we've grown from that first plant to serving customers , and we've committed to planting a tree for every purchase to give back to the environment. the future is promising as we expand our offerings, introduce innovative products, and continue nurturing our community. join us on this green adventure, explore our curated collection, and connect with like-minded enthusiasts.
